<h1 class="has-accent-color has-text-color">Aims &amp; Objectives</h1>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">Rawalpindi Chamber of Commerce and Industries (RCCI) organized a 2 day ‚ÄúDigital Exports Conference and Smart Technology Exhibition‚Äù at PC Rawalpindi to promote local digital industries and IT solution providers.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"align":"left","level":1,"textColor":"accent"} -->
<h1 class="has-accent-color has-text-color has-text-align-left">Goals</h1>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">The honorable Governor Punjab Ch. Muhammad Sawar was the chief guest at the opening ceremony on Feburary 3rd 2020. He visited NUST stall and showed keen interest in our Vehicle Recognition and Verification project. Several other dignitaries visited the expo on the opening day including Chairman PITB, Chairman RCCI, President RCCI, etc. Our goal of projecting our capabilities to the relevant audience has been met with great success and many industries like PTCL, FFC, Greyscale Logic, NewVative Technologies, Asasa Real-estate visited our stall and showed great<br>interest in our products. FFC delegate showed great interest in NCAI projects and have offered potential collaborations to solve their pain points w.r.t. Pakistani agriculture landscape.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"align":"left","level":1,"textColor":"accent"} -->
<h1 class="has-accent-color has-text-color has-text-align-left">Observation &amp; Evaluation</h1>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"left"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-left">The DLL team put a lot of hard work and dedication in representing the NCAI at this prestigious expo. Mr. Tayyab Ali, BDM Marketing was also very helpful in bringing and networking with several industries and potential end-users. The arrangements made by the NUST team, led by Mr. Waseem Mirza (BDM) were also very appreciative. They made every effort to make the participation smooth and hassle free. NUST management also made sure that every product has its beautifully designed flyers.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

